Step 4: Create and Deploy the Lambda Function

bash
aws lambda create-function \
--function-name SalesforceQuery \
--runtime python3.8 # replace with your Python version
--role arn:aws:iam::your-account-id:role/your-lambda-rol \
--handler lambda_function.lambda_handler \
--zip-file fileb://function.zip \
--timeout 15 \
--memory-size 128
